categories: Category:Enlisted stormtroopers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Joak Quiller was a stormtrooper pilot on the Reprisal as of 0.5 ABY. His identification number was TKR 2014. He later became a member of the Hand of Judgment. He was part of Daric LaRone's "party" escaping the Reprisal because of being part of Major Drelfin's death.
